snippet.title: Holdfast: Frontlines WW1 - Gallipoli. Heroes Landing
snippet.description:
Embark to the Gallipoli peninsula with the lads from down under. 

Frontlines is a total-conversion DLC based in the WW1 released for free as a show of thanks to our beloved community. Play today!

- Steam Store (Available Now - 65% Off): https://store.steampowered.com/app/589290
